@page "/"

<PageTitle>Home</PageTitle>

<div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md mt-10">
    <!-- Grid splits your text on the left, and your image on the right -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">

        <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-red-700 mb-6 border-b pb-2">Welcome to Prime Cuts</h1>

            <p>
                Welcome to your premier destination for the finest, hand-selected meats available. We source our products exclusively from local, sustainable farms that prioritize quality, animal welfare, and exceptional taste. Whether you are planning a weekend backyard barbecue, a quiet family dinner, or looking for premium cuts for a special occasion, we have everything you need to make your next meal unforgettable.
            </p>
            <p>
                Our expert butchers take immense pride in their craft, precision-cutting every single piece to ensure optimal tenderness and maximum flavor. From richly marbled USDA Prime beef steaks and succulent heritage pork to fresh, free-range poultry, our inventory is carefully curated daily. We also feature a rotating selection of house-made sausages and specialty smoked meats crafted from old-world family recipes.
            </p>
            <p>
                We believe that shopping for high-quality protein should be simple, transparent, and convenient. Explore our comprehensive selection today, read about our sourcing standards, and place your order directly online for quick, temperature-controlled pickup or local delivery. Experience the difference that true craftsmanship and premium quality bring to your kitchen table.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex justify-center">
            <img src="images/space-steak.png"
                 class="img-fluid rounded-3 shadow-sm single-img max-w-full h-auto"
                 alt="meat" />
        </div>

    </div>
</div>